{"tid":1302352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幫幫手再推！民研仲未籌夠錢！","createTime":"2019-07-10T02:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T02:26:54.000Z","uid":264958,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8548f5eae031924b8957f55c1a7f134e45ae4c21","tid":1302352,"uid":264958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T02:15:55.000Z","msg":"民研計劃由7月1日起轉型為獨立機構「香港民意研究所」，依靠公民捐款維持運作，4月底曾宣佈要一次過籌募600萬元起動基金，惟爆出反惡法風波後，研究所主席鍾庭耀僅指「社會有其他事更需要資源」而主動停止募捐，即使7.1當日經傳媒報道後，當天也只是籌到48萬元，距離目標尚遠。<br />\n<br />\n民研計劃現急需捐款資助，若在3、4日內未能籌得足夠經費，原來每兩星期發佈一次的特首民望調查，將於今個月內「斷纜」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190710/59773000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190710%2F59773000&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=4c41f5a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190710%2F59773000&h=e2003a27\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190710/59773000</a>"},{"pid":"c2062cc517c0514bb4f6e7b0b6f5569da6ab7034","tid":1302352,"uid":34515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T02:18:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c5d569d82b0b832a6effa5cbd61d74af18394a","tid":1302352,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T02:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" clas